machine_end_gcode:
G1 E-1.0 F2100 ; retract
G92 E0.0
G1{if max_layer_z < max_print_height} Z{z_offset+min(max_layer_z+30, max_print_height)}{endif} E-2.0 F720 ; move print head up & retract filament
G4 ; wait
M104 T0 S0 ; turn off temperature
M104 T1 S0 ; turn off temperature
M140 S0 ; turn off heatbed
M107 ; turn off fan

T0
_PARK_TOOL
T1
_PARK_TOOL

;G1 X0 Y105 F3000 ; park print head


M84 ; disable motors
machine_start_gcode:
G90 ; use absolute coordinates
M83 ; extruder relative mode
M204 S[machine_max_acceleration_extruding] T[machine_max_acceleration_retracting]


; ----------- Temperatures ------------------------------
M104 T0 S[first_layer_temperature] ; set extruder temp

{if is_extruder_used[1]}

   M104 T1 S[first_layer_temperature] ;preheat second extruder if used

{endif}

M190 S[first_layer_bed_temperature] ; wait for bed temp

; ----------------- Home and Calibrations ------------------
G28 ; home all
Z_TILT_ADJUST
ADAPTIVE_BED_MESH_CALIBRATE AREA_START={first_layer_print_min[0]},{first_layer_print_min[1]} AREA_END={first_layer_print_max[0]},{first_layer_print_max[1]}
BED_MESH_PROFILE SAVE=default
BED_MESH_PROFILE LOAD=default

; ---------------- Modes ----------------------

;ACTIVATE_COPY_MODE
;ACTIVATE_MIRROR_MODE

M109 S[first_layer_temperature] ; wait for extruder temp
G92 E0.0

; ----------------- Purge Line ------------------------------
G1 X{first_layer_print_min[0]-10} Y{first_layer_print_min[1]} Z0.8 F{initial_layer_travel_speed}
G1 X{first_layer_print_min[0]-10} Y{first_layer_print_min[1]+15} E30 F{bridge_speed}
G29 E0.0
name: Sv04 IDEX
